crophone Effects]\nEnjoy a variety of fun with echo and other microphone effects and karaoke functions.\n\n[A Wide Selection of Songs]\nFrom familiar tunes to new tracks, sing your favorite songs, with new songs added continuously.\n\n[Connecting Through Music]\nEnjoy music solo or engage in multiplayer and social interactions, connecting with new friends through music.\n\nStart your performance and create memories with XR entertainment centered around music", "short_description": "SingRoom is a VR social karaoke.\nEnjoy your favorite songs alone or together in stunning spaces!\nStart your performance and create memories with XR entertainment centered around music"}, {"images": {"nodes": [{"file_name": "Logo_W.png", "id": "2037009236758399", "image_type": "APP_IMG_LOGO_TRANSPARENT", "uri": "https://scontent-iad3-2.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/39001663_2037009240091732_6274024698972295157_n.png?_nc_cat=106&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=g8O-KkZ0u0YQ7kNvgFars2T&_nc_ht=scontent-iad3-2.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYBamkL-9af2CmC8UAo8NnhD8nrsLClbu7SF1tIVNn3Lrw&oe=670E58EF"}, {"file_name": "Mobile Icon_512x512.png", "id": "1662144754347109", "image_type": "APP_IMG_ICON", "uri": "https://scontent-iad3-1.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/57570306_1662144757680442_3047029859871833100_n.png?_nc_cat=102&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=k6oQ7-PxV-0Q7kNvgGE7JfO&_nc_ht=scontent-iad3-1.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYCqo0F9V5t-8xEBEvQgqpEbB5e5G8012MUOukRLtJ8GuQ&oe=670E56CF"}, {"file_name": "Landscape_2560x1440.png", "id": "1455643215096373", "image_type": "APP_IMG_COVER_LANDSCAPE", "uri": "https://scontent-iad3-1.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/38974861_1455643218429706_4847338792641025967_n.png?_nc_cat=104&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=cDcihAIbK-QQ7kNvgHOlm_X&_nc_ht=scontent-iad3-1.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYCxBTxNJRNVVOdgmBXdDN8vTKejwH0IWG_eObRZJ5mDFQ&oe=670E50F4"}, {"file_name": "Portrait_1008x1440.png", "id": "526393913280535", "image_type": "APP_IMG_COVER_PORTRAIT", "uri": "https://scontent-iad3-1.oculuscdn.co